## 📊 mongo-task-2(Mongodb queries)

A complete collection of MongoDB queries covering topics, tasks, company drives, placements, mentors, codekata problems, and attendance case studies.

---
## 🚀 Features

- MongoDB queries for real-world scenarios

- Covers topics, tasks, company drives, placements, codekata problems, mentors, and attendance

- Aggregation pipelines with $lookup, $match, $group, $project, and $count

- Hands-on practice with date filtering and relationships between collections

---

## 📂 Project Structure
mongo-task-2/
 ├── database
 │ ├── design
 ├── readme
---

## 🔗 Clone
```bash
git clone https://github.com/Elanthiran/mongo-task-2.git
cd mongo-task-2
```
---

## 🛠️ Usage

- Install MongoD

- Import your dataset into MongoDB collections (topics, tasks, users, companydrives, codekata, attendance)

- Open Mongo shell and run queries from the queries/ folder

